						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/APAARI-Newsletter-Vol.-20-No.-1-June-2011" title="APAARI Newsletter, Vol. 20, No. 1, June 2011" alt="link">APAARI Newsletter, Vol. 20, No. 1, June 2011</a></h2>

	
					<p>A content rich newsletter from the Asia-Pacific Association of Agricultural Research Institutions (APAARI)that discusses APAARI’s and APCoAB’S high level committee meetings, rapid bioassay of pesticide residue, GM food crops, CIARD in the SAARC Countries, the new CAPSA institution, upcoming events and much more.</p>
							<p><span class="date">2/11/2011</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/APAARI-Newsletter-Vol.-20-No.-1-June-2011">Read more...</a>
</div>
<br class="cl">
